# Snake Game üêç

A classic Snake game built with Pygame. The player controls a snake that grows with each apple collected, avoiding collisions with the walls or itself.

## Features
- Real-time movement with arrow keys
- Apple spawning and score tracking
- Collision detection and game over screen

## Technologies
- Python
- Turtle

## What I learned
- Handling game loops and frame rates
- Using external libraries (`turtle`)
- Basic collision and event detection

## Run the game
```bash
python snake.py
